`hexo server` to start local hexo server

---

In order to stop loading disqus while writing a post, go to:

themes/tranquilpeak/layout/_partial/script.ejs and comment out the disqus script starting at line 8.

Remember to uncomment it before deploying...

---

You need to clone https://github.com/justincalleja/tranquilpeak-hexo-theme.git

into your themes/ directory as `tranquilpeak`:

```
themes $ git clone https://github.com/justincalleja/tranquilpeak-hexo-theme.git tranquilpeak
```

Install hexo globally with `npm i -g hexo-cli`
